"tid":576004,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味，我地打工仔日日返工，年年交税就乜柒都無，人地乜撚都唔駛做，訓覺訓到肩周炎就有雙糧三糧，公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n香港已經由以前多勞多得，變成而家不勞而穫"},{"pid":"b734fe1155a7688c73f2a81bbd1ebc8020bcb9ec","tid":576004,"uid":130351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似我呢啲低頭密密做自食其力死慳死抵，係樓市苦海掙扎求存嘅就永撚遠無份享用呢啲派糖措施<br />\n相反嗰啲日日訓到日上三竿，過住食訓屌生活嘅老綜大陸畜就次撚次有得啜資源嗓到盡<br />\n你老母班傻尻高官咪繼續養埋一大班懶尻囉，到時咪撚埋怨點解香港人嘅質素同生產力會大不如前，因為就係呢啲不公平派糖措施話比香港市民知，努力工作先係傻仔，好食懶飛咬老綜霸公屋先係皇道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6407dcd20baa57f51efd4d51bb5bcff68b46a52","tid":576004,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd7004c6f5d55775e1aa70d2e0859eba5ad4950","tid":576004,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"我同班同事討論,個個都同意我話三糧應該派撚埋俾班同事<br />\n屌你老母啦,好食懶飛果班綜援狗都三糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8464608ae4cf8ab39cb1ac7d9f49706d4f8ffd1","tid":576004,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"公務員一直都無雙糧，不如今次整個雙糧俾佢地啦"},{"pid":"d6afff7118c6fa81fc11ffb9d3dd6861d0c0c1ba","tid":576004,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8464608ae4cf8ab39cb1ac7d9f49706d4f8ffd1","tid":576004,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"公務員一直都無雙糧，不如今次整個雙糧俾佢地啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:10:31.00